            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报9,720.55点，升9.68点(0.10%)；德国DAX指数报23,970.29点，升88.26点(0.37%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,138.17点，升16.14点(0.20%)。 <br/> (WL)</span>\n</div>",
